# xclarity_room_to_location — map XClarity location.room values to NetBox location names
# Format: regex_pattern,replacement
# Lines starting with # are ignored.
# The first matching pattern wins; the original value is returned unchanged if nothing matches.
#
# Examples:
#   ^Room101$,Server Room A
#   ^Room202$,Server Room B
#   (?i)^mdf.*,Main Distribution Frame
